data.description: A Joy to Show!  Location at its BEST, Easy Access to 83, PA Turnpike, Rt 30, 581 and 81.  Parks, shopping, public transportation, restaurants and local New Cumberland fare are right around the corner too.  This Beautifully Renovated and Updated home is just waiting on new memories.   New Paint, Floors, Lighting, and a gorgeous, Lush Yard.  An outstanding Bi-Level in a desirable neighborhood has everything you ever wanted, Privacy, large Open floor plan, bright natural lighting,3 freshly painted and newly carpeted bedrooms, 2 full, updated bathrooms, and Dining Room leading to a large deck overlooking the rear of the property into the woods.  A perfect way to start or end your day....serenity.  The whole upstairs has beautiful hardwood floors and cathedral ceilings in the living space, newer Furnace and AC, fully Finished lower level with so many possibilities, Just ready for your imagination--- This space could be decorated into smaller areas with plenty of storage, and laundry room.  This could be a Teen Suite or In-Laws Quarters, or Game room leading right out onto a beautiful patio.  This would be a perfect setting with a little lighting and soft music.  Let your Creativity come alive.  A Clean 1 Car Garage and Private Rear Yard with Plenty of Room to Play.  Your Own private oasis tucked away with Deer, Birds and a Whole Upper Level for a Bon-Fire, a Shed, or Sledding.  Possibilities are Endless.  Worried About Winter Storms Knocking Out Your Electric, Worry No More..... Propane Gas Back-Up Heater in the Lower Family Room!  Call me Today for a Private Tour.  Motivated Sellers, Bring your Holiday Cheer and Offers Today.
